{"tid":2436974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"47民主派被控︱黃碧雲提醒夫幫忙交稅","createTime":"2021-03-07T14:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T14:17:55.000Z","uid":10199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da0ba350b6d88e94eab40f5479a40f3434b390cb","tid":2436974,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"47名民主派因去年參與民主派初選被控「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」，其中何桂藍及黃碧雲於大欖女懲教所羈留。她們的親友下午前往探望。黃碧雲丈夫指黃精神不俗，已為妻子準備數本書，讓她在獄中解悶。雖然被政府政治檢控，黃碧雲仍不忘提醒丈夫，幫她向庫房交稅。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲夫冀周四再上庭有好消息<br />\n<br />\n佘雲楚探望黃碧雲後，指她精神不俗，惟15分鐘探訪時間不長，未有多談還柙的情況。被問到伙食如何，佘笑道「好唔好都要哽啦」，又指黃已向福利官申請私飯。佘續稱，前日曾與黃胞兄探望黃碧雲，當時對方已吩咐他打理家頭細務，提醒他協助交稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/ENE63Q63BVFOFAEBLOWYCIAXMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FENE63Q63BVFOFAEBLOWYCIAXMQ%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=cc336ba2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FENE63Q63BVFOFAEBLOWYCIAXMQ%2F&h=72b5e268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/ENE63Q63BVFOFAEBLOWYCIAXMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"df2e9f2856f5cb9acc79d67e9b8de547f7653d4f","tid":2436974,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"仲交稅，係唔係痴撚線"},{"pid":"95b4da1c3710ed160041363ef9f447ef8d887683","tid":2436974,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2e9f2856f5cb9acc79d67e9b8de547f7653d4f","tid":2436974,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"仲交稅，係唔係痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae41b05bf1d5de97ab00331a48fe287acb2